Operation Manager
Responsibilities
In order to be succesful in this role you must commit your past expreince with willigness to learn and succeed. The role requires attention to detail, frequent travelling across Indonesia and maximising the use of resources. As this is a retail based company we require hard motivated personnel, target focused and able to motivate ground staff in order to reach customer satifcation and meet targets. The succesful candiate will be supported in his role to make it success. Our company values honesty, hard work, loyalty and fun work environment where problems easily meet solutions. English speaking is an advantage but not an requirement. If you think you have what it takes CLICK the button below and apply.Candidate must possess at least a Diploma, Bachelor's Degree, Master's Degree / Post Graduate Degree, Food & Beverage Services Management or equivalent.At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Applicants must be willing to work in SURABAYA.Preferably Manager / Assistant Managers specializing in Food/Beverage/Restaurant Service or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.
